author: Paul Cullen, Jack Horgan-Jones
title: Coronavirus: Irish death rate from Covid-19 rises to 2.4% of cases
description: It will take 10 days to reach testing goal, Minister says
content:
Taoiseach Leo Varadkar has said there will be delays in Covid-19 tests and results in the coming weeks.
